<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="styles.css">
    <title>Categories</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        header nav ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
        }

        header nav ul li {
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        header nav ul li a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        main {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-around;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .category {
            width: 300px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .category img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .category h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .category p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #666;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;">
            <img src="images/logo.png" alt="Warner Bros Logo" style="height: 40px; margin-right: 20px;">
            <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">Warner Bros</h1>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="movies.html">Movies</a></li>
                    <li><a href="shows.html">TV Shows</a></li>
                    <li><a href="games.html">Games & Apps</a></li>
                    <li><a href="collections.html">Collections</a></li>
                    <li><a href="feedback.html">Feedback</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

<main>
    <div class="category">
        <img src="images/action.jpg" alt="Action">
        <h2>Action</h2>
        <p>Get your adrenaline pumping with thrilling action-packed movies and shows. From epic battles to high-speed chases, our action collection is sure to keep you 
		on the edge of your seat. Experience the excitement and explosive entertainment of action-packed adventures.</p>
        <a href="action.html" class="category-link">Explore Action</a>
    </div>
    <div class="category">
        <img src="images/romance.jpg" alt="Romance">
        <h2>Romance</h2>
        <p>Discover heartwarming stories and fall in love with our romantic collection. Immerse yourself in tales of passionate love, tender moments, and sweeping romances.
		Whether you're in the mood for a classic love story or a charming romantic comedy, our collection will make your heart flutter.</p>
        <a href="romance.html" class="category-link">Explore Romance</a>
    </div>
    <div class="category">
        <img src="images/scifi.jpg" alt="Sci-Fi">
        <h2>Sci-Fi</h2>
        <p>Embark on futuristic journeys and explore the unknown with our sci-fi titles. From mind-bending concepts to thrilling adventures in distant galaxies, 
		our sci-fi collection will transport you to other worlds. Experience the wonders of advanced technology, encounter alien species, and delve into the possibilities of the future.</p>
        <a href="sci-fi.html" class="category-link">Explore Sci-Fi</a>
    </div>
